n there?  Everyone knows that PvP sucks and why would you subject yourself to all that pain?&quot;  <br>
<br>
Well ladies and gentlemen, I believe we have a convert.  I will be making a barb rogue on one of the PvP servers, prob SZ but I am open to suggestions. <br>
<br>
I just couldn't get my mind around the idea of someone looting my corpse and taking &quot;X&quot; loot off me.  I don't want to leave EQ but the emphasis on lvl and loot has kinda got me down.  I think that on the PvP servers where the risk, that seemed overwhelming before, will be just what the doctor ordered.<br>
<br>
<br>
